<NEW>

At the moment the larger bulkier figure was still standing over the
protohumans making them work, forcing them to dig into the rock,
occasionally extracting glowing stones that were put into a carrier.

The noise they were making was loud enough that apparently they did
not hear PERCEPTOR's knocking on the rock or his digging.

Suddenly the bulkier figure disappeared from view as he fell through a
hole in the ground created by PERCEPTOR's tunnel, as he hit the ground
he was apparently stunned as he did not move.

The figure was dressed in some sort of suit, a radiation suit. The
figure was human!

(TAG)

- Preston
